<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Verity cut to neutral.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Verity cut to neutral.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Alex. Brown said Verity Inc was downgraded to neutral from buy.</p>
<p>-- shares plummeted 11-3/8 to 12-3/4.</p>
<p>-- company said on Thursday it expected to post a loss of $1.3 million, or $0.12 per share, in the first fiscal quarter, ended Aug 31.</p>
